## 2026-03-29 18:39:51 +1100
- Command: refine-ui
- Title: Design system + UX/UI guidance refinement
- Decision: Add a compact UI signature and refine core design-system guidance (principles, hierarchy, spacing, color, typography, motion, templates, responsive rules) to encode a calm, systems-first style.
- Rationale: Existing guidance was generic and under-specified; the refinements align the system to the stated influences and reduce drift toward card-heavy SaaS defaults while preserving the existing structure.

## 2026-03-29 18:51:27 +1100
- Command: refine-ui
- Title: Action recommendations: component rules + archetypes + token values
- Decision: Add component usage rules for list rows, inspectors, and sheets; add UI archetypes; codify a neutral-first token palette with semantic mappings.
- Rationale: These additions translate the style intent into actionable composition guidance and concrete tokens, reducing future drift while keeping the existing system lightweight.

